        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Calculated value. 
	
There are many different specific types of cement present in the ecoinvent database. It is estimated, that 20% of these specific types can be replaced by another type of cement. The sum of all production volumes feeding the generic market for cement, unspecified /CH is 8.35E+08 kg.	

Total production volume of cement in Switzerland in 2021: 4'177'000 metric ton. Source: cemsuisse (2022), Jahresbericht cemsuisse 2022, page 9. Available at: https://www.cemsuisse.ch/jahresberichte/, accessed on 20230620.

The total exports in 2019 of cement from Switzerland were 2.01E+08 kg (4.8% of the production). Out of that 99.98% was exported to other European countries. The total imports in 2021 of cement to Switzerland were 7.00E+08 kg (14.36% from the total amount consumed). Out of that 99.95% was imported from other European countries. Source: trade statistics of Switzerland 2021. Available at: https://www.swiss-impex.admin.ch/pages/bereiche/waren/result.xhtml (accessed 20231005)
	
The ratio between local Swiss production of cement, unspecified (8.35E+08 kg) and imports from the European market is 84:16, resulting in 1.36E+08 kg production volume of the import.	

</productionVolumeComment>
